<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/>
</head>

<body>
<div>
  <% if @local_language == "en" %>
      <p>Dear Approver,</p>

      <p>You can reply YES or NO to process this request directly. Or click the below link to login to the system to
        process.</p>

      <p>*YES represents Approved, NO represents Rejected. (Case insensitive)</p>

      <p>Link: http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/en/clients/<%= @client.id %>?examination_id=<%= @examination_id %></p>

      <%= render 'client_template', {client: @client, local_language: @local_language} %>
      <p>If any enquiries, please contact: technology@i-click.com</p>

      <p>Regards,</p>

      <p>iClick Interactive Asia Limited</p>

  <% else %>
      <p>您好:</p>

      <p>* 您可以直接回复YES或NO进行审批，或可以点击下方的链接登录系统进行审批。</p>

      <p>*YES表示审批通过，NO表示审批不通过，不区分大小写。</p>

      <p>链接：http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/zh-cn/clients/<%= @client.id %>?examination_id=<%= @examination_id %></p>

      <%= render 'client_template', {client: @client, local_language: @local_language} %>
      <p>如有问题，请联系: technology@i-click.com</p>

      <p>谢谢</p>

      <p>爱点击互动（北京）广告有限公司</p>
  <% end %>
</div>
</body>
</html>